    <h2>What we do for commercial food processors, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> Robot Coupe R-series (R2, R4, R8, R10, R15, R30), Hobart buffalo choppers (84142, 84186), Univex countertop and floor food processors, Vitamix Commercial high-volume blenders. Blade sharpening and NSF-listed OEM replacement, motor brush service (Robot Coupe brushed motors), motor replacement, safety interlock service, bowl latch service, drive coupling, drive belt, bowl bearing rebuild (Hobart buffalo).</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> industrial food processing systems (specialty industrial trade with multi-station continuous-feed architectures); knife and blade sharpening pickup-and-return service (we do on-site work, not separate sharpening route service); commercial juice extractors with hydraulic press architectures (specialty trade). New food processor installation we coordinate but don't perform; specialty installer trade.</p>
